name: Winged Kuriboh LV9
effectText: Activate only as Chain Link 3 or higher (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon this card from your hand. Spell Cards that have been activated are banished instead of being sent to the GY. The ATK/DEF of this card are each equal to the number of Spells in your opponent's GY x 500. You can only control 1 "Winged Kuriboh LV9".
